# Auth + Draft Flow Lock

- Keep this login sequence unchanged unless explicitly requested:
  1) show loading text after Google login
  2) complete `/api/registry/ensure`
  3) show confirm dialog with Google email and require clicking `確定`
  4) then enter consent and writing pages
- Keep draft auto-fill on login in `ApplicationForm`:
  - must call `/api/draft` on mount
  - must hydrate `formData` from returned draft
- Do not remove session keys used by this flow:
  - `sbir_registry_ensure_email`
  - `sbir_login_dialog_ok`
- For later feature edits, avoid changing this flow behavior.
